import { Box, Grid, TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material';
import React from 'react'
import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom'

export default function OrderDetails() {
    const {id} = useParams();
    return (
        <Box sx={{mt: "150px"}} className="container">
        <Grid container>
            <Grid item lg={8} className="container" >
                <Box sx={{boxShadow: 1, borderRadius: '5px', p:'15px', background:'#fdfdfd'}}>
                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'17px'}}>Shipping Address</Typography>
                    <Box sx={{mt:'25px'}}>
                        <Grid container>
                                <Grid item lg={5.8}>
                                    <TextField size={"small"} helperText={"Please Enter your name"} label={"Name"} onChange={ (e)=>setName(e.target.value) } variant={"outlined"} style={{width: '100%'}}/>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item lg={0.4}></Grid>
                                <Grid item lg={5.8} sx={{mb: "35px"}}>
                                    <Input size={"small"} helperText={"Please Enter your Email Address"} label={"Email"} onChange={ (e)=>setEmail(e.target.value) } variant={"outlined"} style={{width: '100%'}}/>
                                </Grid>
                                    <Grid item lg={5.8}>
                                        <Input size={"small"} helperText={"Please Enter your Phone Number"} label={"Number"} onChange={ (e)=>setNumber(e.target.value) } variant={"outlined"} style={{width: '100%'}}/>
                                    </Grid>
                                    <Grid item lg={0.4}></Grid>
                                    <Grid item lg={5.8} sx={{mb: "35px"}}>
                                        <Input size={"small"} helperText={"Please Enter your Company (optional)"} label={"Company"}  variant={"outlined"} style={{width: '100%'}}/>
                                    </Grid>
                                <Grid item lg={5.8}>
                                    <Input size={"small"} helperText={"Please Enter your Zip Code"} label={"Zip Code"} onChange={ (e)=>setCode(e.target.value) } variant={"outlined"} style={{width: '100%'}}/>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item lg={0.4}></Grid>
                                <Grid item lg={5.8} sx={{mb: "35px"}}>
                                    <Input size={"small"} helperText={"Please Enter your Country"} label={"Country"} variant={"outlined"} style={{width: '100%'}}/>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item lg={5.8}>
                                    <Input size={"small"} helperText={"Please Enter your Adress"} label={"Address 1"} onChange={ (e)=>setAddress(e.target.value) } variant={"outlined"} style={{width: '100%'}}/>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item lg={0.4}></Grid>
                                <Grid item lg={5.8} sx={{mb: "35px"}}>
                                    <Input size={"small"} helperText={"Please Enter your Adress"} label={"Adress 2"} variant={"outlined"} style={{width: '100%'}}/>
                                </Grid>
                        
                        </Grid>
                    </Box>
                </Box>

                <Grid container>
                    <Grid item lg={12}>
                    <Box sx={{boxShadow: 1, borderRadius: '5px', p:'15px', background:'#fdfdfd', mt:"40px"}}>
                        <FormControl>
                            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'17px', p:"10px"}} fullWidth>Payment</Typography>
                            <RadioGroup
                                aria-labelledby="demo-radio-buttons-group-label"
                                name="radio-buttons-group">
                                <FormControlLabel value="female" control={<Radio/>} label="Cash on Delivery" sx={{p:"5px"}}/>
                                <FormControlLabel value="male" control={<Radio/>} label="Pay with credit card" sx={{p:"5px"}} />
                            </RadioGroup>
                        </FormControl>
                    </Box>
                    </Grid>

                </Grid>

                <Grid container sx={{mt: '30px'}}>
                    <Grid item lg={5.8}>
                        <Box>
                        <Link to="/cart" className="nav-link"><SubmitButton text={"Back to Card"} style={{width: '100%'}} variant={"outlined"}/></Link>

                        </Box>
                    </Grid>
                        <Grid item lg={0.4}></Grid>
                        <Grid item lg={5.8} sx={{mb: "30px"}}>
                            {/* <Button variant="contained" fullWidth onClick={SuccessOrder}>Place Order</Button> */}
                            <SubmitButton text={"Place Order"} style={{width: '100%'}} variant={"contained"} onClick={SuccessOrder} />
                        </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item lg={4}>
                <Box sx={{boxShadow: 1, borderRadius: '5px', p:'15px', background:'#fdfdfd'}}>
                    {/* <Box sx={{display:'flex'}}> */}
                    <Grid container sx={{mt:'20px'}}>
                        <Grid item lg={6}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'14px', mt:'2px'}} align="left">Subtotal:</Typography>                    
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item lg={6}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'17px', fontWeight: 'bold'}} align="right">${grandTotal}</Typography>
                        </Grid>
                    
                        <Grid item lg={6} sx={{mt:'5px'}} >
                            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'14px', mt:'2px'}} align="left">Shipping:</Typography>                    
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item lg={6} sx={{mt:'5px'}}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'17px', fontWeight: 'bold'}} align="right">-</Typography>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item lg={6} sx={{mt:'5px'}} >
                            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'14px', mt:'2px'}} align="left">Tax:</Typography>                    
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item lg={6} sx={{mt:'5px'}}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'17px', fontWeight: 'bold'}} align="right">-</Typography>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item lg={6} sx={{mt:'5px'}} >
                            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'14px', mt:'2px'}} align="left">Discount:</Typography>                    
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item lg={6} sx={{mt:'5px'}}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'17px', fontWeight: 'bold'}} align="right">-</Typography>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item lg = {12} sx={{mt:'5px'}}>
                            <Box sx={{borderBottom: "1px solid #c4c4c4"}}></Box>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item lg={6} sx={{mt:'5px'}} >
                            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'17px',fontWeight: 'bold'}} align="left">Grandtotal:</Typography>                    
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item lg={6} sx={{mt:'5px'}}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontSize:'17px', fontWeight: 'bold'}} align="right">${grandTotal}</Typography>
                        </Grid>
                    </Grid>
                        {/* </Box> */}

                </Box>
            </Grid>
            <Box sx={{height:"1px",borderBottom: "1px soild grey"}}></Box>

        </Grid>
    </Box>
    )
}
